en_177410_0	The Ministry of Home Affairs says that part of the compensation to be provided to those affected by natural disasters will be paid today (02).
en_177410_1	Minister of Home Affairs Vajira Abeywardena said, therefore, all District Secretariats and Divisional Secretariats will be kept open today and tomorrow to facilitate this.
en_177410_2	Accordingly, the affected people whose houses have been damaged will be able to obtain an advance payment out of the total compensation due to them.
en_177410_3	Meanwhile, the Minister said that the people can inform the Ministry of any emergency situation through the number 1902.
